Class Organization

java.lang.Object
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Thing
com.iunera.jsonldjava.schemaorg.metadatatypes.Organization
Direct Known Subclasses:
Airline, Corporation, EducationalOrganization, GovernmentOrganization, LocalBusiness, MedicalOrganization, NGO, PerformingGroup, SportsOrganization
public abstract class Organization extends Thing
An organization such as a school, NGO, corporation, club, etc.
